WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:46.879 --> 00:01:47.840
Where are you going?

00:01:50.599 --> 00:01:51.480
Out on a case.

00:01:51.920 --> 00:01:52.760
I'm coming with you.

00:01:52.760 --> 00:01:53.840
Why would I take you along?

00:01:57.879 --> 00:01:58.560
Let's settle this

00:01:58.560 --> 00:01:59.719
once and for all today.

00:02:01.640 --> 00:02:02.959
From now on,

00:02:02.959 --> 00:02:03.799
quit tailing me everywhere

00:02:04.519 --> 00:02:05.920
and stay out of my business.

00:02:07.319 --> 00:02:08.719
Don't flatter yourself either.

00:02:10.360 --> 00:02:11.240
Just because lately
I've been going easy on you

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:14.080
doesn't mean I'm into you.

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:16.479
Go back

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:18.360
where you came from.

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:21.199
You're not investigating a case at all.

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:22.560
You just want to go with Gu Jinzhao

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:24.199
to the border to find Chen Yanyun, right?

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:26.719
None of your business.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:27.919
Move!
No!

00:02:32.039 --> 00:02:33.080
The border's dangerous.

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:34.560
That whole envoy vanished
without a trace.

00:02:36.240 --> 00:02:37.400
Just you and Li Xianhuai alone?

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:38.199
No way that'll work…
Miss!

00:02:41.919 --> 00:02:42.840
Miss,

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:44.360
Master's orders.

00:02:44.439 --> 00:02:46.360
Please return home at once.

00:02:51.199 --> 00:02:52.800
You told my father?

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:55.479
Miss, please.

00:02:59.479 --> 00:03:00.319
I'm not going back.

00:03:00.680 --> 00:03:01.400
Get lost, all of you!

00:03:01.680 --> 00:03:02.759
Then forgive us

00:03:02.759 --> 00:03:03.520
for being rough.

00:03:04.240 --> 00:03:04.840
Do it!

00:03:07.759 --> 00:03:08.520
Let go of me!

00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:10.759
Ye Xian!

00:03:11.240 --> 00:03:12.439
Ye Xian, come back!

00:03:12.639 --> 00:03:13.439
You can't go!

00:03:14.319 --> 00:03:15.159
Ye Xian!

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:16.599
Move!
Let go of me!

00:03:17.520 --> 00:03:19.360
Hyah!

00:03:30.919 --> 00:03:31.840
You okay?

00:03:34.280 --> 00:03:35.039
Help me up.

00:03:36.199 --> 00:03:36.680
Sir.
Well?

00:03:37.319 --> 00:03:38.400
Hear anything useful?

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:39.639
Why are there so many refugees?

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:40.800
We figured it out.

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:42.080
They all came from Shi City.

00:03:42.479 --> 00:03:43.120
They say a large group
of Chunyuan remnants

00:03:43.960 --> 00:03:45.680
came out of nowhere
and attacked the envoy.

00:03:46.039 --> 00:03:47.800
Over 100 people
are now missing or dead.

00:03:47.960 --> 00:03:49.120
Some say the remnants

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:50.159
dragged them into the northern steppe.

00:03:50.360 --> 00:03:51.639
Others say they were all killed

00:03:51.639 --> 00:03:52.759
and dumped in the mountains.

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:53.919
The border trade was fine,

00:03:53.919 --> 00:03:54.960
but now it's gone haywire too.

00:03:55.199 --> 00:03:56.280
Everyone's saying war's coming,

00:03:56.280 --> 00:03:57.520
so people are fleeing south.

00:03:58.879 --> 00:04:00.159
Tell the men to stay sharp,

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:01.199
we're almost at Shi City.

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:02.240
Yes.

00:04:02.840 --> 00:04:04.080
Also, sir.

00:04:04.479 --> 00:04:05.960
Up ahead is Bitter Ridge.

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:07.599
Since ancient times most who crossed it

00:04:07.599 --> 00:04:08.759
never came back.

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:09.759
The men…

00:04:10.319 --> 00:04:11.639
are pretty shaken up.

00:04:14.719 --> 00:04:15.520
Tell everyone

00:04:16.759 --> 00:04:17.759
this trip's pay

00:04:17.959 --> 00:04:18.839
will be tripled.

00:04:19.160 --> 00:04:20.160
And if we make it back safe,

00:04:21.279 --> 00:04:22.000
the Ji family
will add another

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:24.240
hundred taels of silver per man.

00:04:24.839 --> 00:04:25.920
Let all stand prepared

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:26.879
and dread not the path ahead.
Yes.

00:04:27.959 --> 00:04:28.480
Yes.

00:05:37.519 --> 00:05:38.000
Sir.

00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:39.879
Both groups of bandits are cleared out.

00:05:40.160 --> 00:05:40.920
Miss Gu's caravan

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:42.160
just needs to pass within four hours

00:05:42.399 --> 00:05:43.439
and they'll be safe.

00:05:44.480 --> 00:05:45.040
Got it.

00:05:46.319 --> 00:05:46.800
Let's go.

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:47.800
Yes.

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:50.240
Sir,

00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:52.360
I really gotta ask.

00:05:52.959 --> 00:05:53.639
We've been clearing the road
for Miss Gu this whole way,

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:55.839
what's so secret about it?

00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:57.439
Why keep it from her

00:05:57.639 --> 00:05:58.800
and go separately instead of together?

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:01.360
If she knows

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:02.600
I'm going with her,

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:04.560
she'll do everything
she can to push me away.

00:06:06.079 --> 00:06:07.120
So instead of that,

00:06:07.959 --> 00:06:09.439
I might as well go ahead of her,

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:10.439
and clear the way for her.

00:06:11.399 --> 00:06:12.319
Once we reach Shi City,

00:06:12.319 --> 00:06:13.360
we can show up.

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:28.600
No rooms left either?

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:29.439
Just wanna talk about that.

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:31.319
This is the only inn in Shi City.

00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:32.319
First they said no rooms

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:33.680
and no price would change that.

00:06:34.040 --> 00:06:35.439
Then the Ji name

00:06:35.439 --> 00:06:36.360
got me two,

00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:37.639
just vacated.

00:06:37.920 --> 00:06:38.920
Isn't that odd?

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:03.839
Sir.

00:07:18.839 --> 00:07:20.439
Only now that I'm in Shi City do I realize

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:22.480
the envoy massacre

00:07:22.480 --> 00:07:23.319
really happened.

00:07:23.639 --> 00:07:24.519
And the city governor here

00:07:24.519 --> 00:07:25.759
has actually gone
into mourning duty at this time.

00:07:26.079 --> 00:07:27.519
And the court even approved it!

00:07:28.120 --> 00:07:30.399
No way that's a coincidence!

00:07:37.680 --> 00:07:38.199
Sir,

00:07:38.879 --> 00:07:40.240
I shouldn't say this, but…

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:41.279
Can you stop

00:07:41.279 --> 00:07:42.319
only worrying about Miss Gu

00:07:42.439 --> 00:07:43.720
and take care of yourself a little too?

00:07:44.120 --> 00:07:45.399
You're coughing like this

00:07:45.399 --> 00:07:46.079
- and still…
- Enough.

00:07:46.759 --> 00:07:48.480
Who said I care about Gu Jinzhao?

00:07:49.560 --> 00:07:50.240
I care about

00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:51.680
the Great Yan empire.

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:53.319
Someone!

00:07:53.519 --> 00:07:54.560
Help!

00:07:54.759 --> 00:07:55.399
Gu Jinzhao!

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:00.199
Gu Jinzhao!

00:08:09.439 --> 00:08:10.199
Ye Xian.

00:08:58.320 --> 00:08:59.360
What a coincidence.

00:08:59.919 --> 00:09:00.960
Of all places, I still ran into you here.

00:09:26.600 --> 00:09:27.879
Chen Yanyun'll be fine.

00:09:28.360 --> 00:09:29.440
Don't worry too much.

00:09:30.759 --> 00:09:31.799
Tomorrow I'll leave the city

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.159
and try again

00:09:33.600 --> 00:09:34.440
to gather more information.

00:09:35.279 --> 00:09:36.240
Listen to me.

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:38.000
At dawn tomorrow,

00:09:38.399 --> 00:09:39.519
you and Mr. Li

00:09:39.879 --> 00:09:41.360
take everyone back to the capital.

00:09:44.039 --> 00:09:45.200
Why should I listen to you?

00:09:46.279 --> 00:09:47.200
I came this time

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:49.279
to go beyond the border and look for him.

00:09:52.039 --> 00:09:52.679
I know.

00:09:53.480 --> 00:09:54.679
If I can't find him there,

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:56.320
I'll head north,

00:09:56.919 --> 00:09:58.360
straight to the Northern
Barbarians' royal camp.

00:10:00.639 --> 00:10:01.440
I know that too.

00:10:03.799 --> 00:10:05.200
Do you even understand what I'm saying?

00:10:05.720 --> 00:10:07.240
It's dangerous following me like this!

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:08.759
You are
not alone,

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:11.120
you still have Madam Ye

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:12.120
and my Fifth Aunt.

00:10:12.879 --> 00:10:14.120
Don't be so reckless, okay?

00:10:15.840 --> 00:10:16.480
I'm tired.

00:10:17.159 --> 00:10:18.120
I'll go rest in my room.

00:10:25.960 --> 00:10:26.679
What's that sound?

00:10:27.000 --> 00:10:28.000
It's the city gate alarm.

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:33.639
Sir,

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:34.679
a large force is approaching

00:10:34.679 --> 00:10:35.919
from the north.

00:10:36.200 --> 00:10:37.039
We need to pull back now.

00:10:37.039 --> 00:10:38.600
Could it be the Northern
Barbarian troops?

00:10:39.360 --> 00:10:39.879
Jinzhao!

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:42.240
This looks serious,

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:43.200
we have to leave.
I can't leave.

00:10:45.080 --> 00:10:45.639
Sir.

00:10:46.240 --> 00:10:47.320
The city governor has fled.

00:10:47.799 --> 00:10:49.279
The city's full of soldiers

00:10:49.799 --> 00:10:50.840
but no leadership.

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:52.879
Since I'm here,
I can't just walk away.

00:10:54.519 --> 00:10:55.080
Li Xianhuai,

00:10:55.399 --> 00:10:56.240
get pen and ink, write a letter

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:57.559
warning Men Plateau and Yi County.

00:10:58.440 --> 00:10:58.879
Quick!
Yes!

00:11:00.159 --> 00:11:00.799
Ye Xian,

00:11:02.080 --> 00:11:03.080
I can't escort you anymore.

00:11:03.320 --> 00:11:04.399
I'm going to the garrison office.

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.519
If we're lucky, the troops
might still hold.

00:11:07.720 --> 00:11:08.279
You leave now,
the faster, the better.

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:10.159
Head south.

00:11:10.679 --> 00:11:11.240
But…
No "buts"!

00:11:12.639 --> 00:11:13.720
I'm from a martial honor family of Great Yan,

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:15.279
I won't abandon the city and run.

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:16.399
Go now.

00:11:18.159 --> 00:11:18.639
Alright.

00:11:19.399 --> 00:11:20.879
Take care of yourself.

00:11:21.360 --> 00:11:22.480
I'll wait for you in Men Plateau.

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:31.000
[Northern Barbarians are invading.]

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:32.720
[Looks like an unannounced war.]

00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:03.960
Hyah!

00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:08.080
Hyah!

00:12:17.759 --> 00:12:18.360
Hyah!

00:12:31.799 --> 00:12:32.759
Yao!

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:34.840
Yao!

00:12:46.960 --> 00:12:48.200
[Where is this?]

00:12:56.879 --> 00:12:57.879
What are you doing?

00:13:11.480 --> 00:13:12.559
What are you doing?

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:15.399
Let go of me!

00:13:16.120 --> 00:13:17.039
Let go!

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:26.240
Don't come any closer!

00:13:30.679 --> 00:13:31.879
Stay back!

00:13:39.000 --> 00:13:39.879
Let me go!

00:13:40.200 --> 00:13:41.240
Let me go!

00:13:41.799 --> 00:13:43.039
Let me!

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:18.840
[Yanyun…]

00:14:22.720 --> 00:14:23.480
[Most of my men]

00:14:24.080 --> 00:14:25.000
[have followed me]

00:14:25.159 --> 00:14:26.360
[for years.]

00:14:27.559 --> 00:14:28.399
[Most of them]

00:14:29.159 --> 00:14:30.000
[are pretty skilled.]

00:14:31.120 --> 00:14:32.200
[If anything happens again,]

00:14:33.480 --> 00:14:34.879
[blow this whistle.]

00:15:45.679 --> 00:15:46.559
Yanyun.

00:15:47.039 --> 00:15:48.480
Why are you so late?

00:15:54.039 --> 00:15:56.519
Why did you take so long?

00:16:56.919 --> 00:16:57.639
Jinzhao,

00:16:58.399 --> 00:16:59.600
I'll take you back.

00:17:07.319 --> 00:17:07.839
Thank you.

00:17:10.839 --> 00:17:11.440
Thank you.

00:17:12.200 --> 00:17:12.720
Barely escaped

00:17:12.720 --> 00:17:13.880
the chaos

00:17:13.880 --> 00:17:14.640
in the trade city.
Thank you.

00:17:15.559 --> 00:17:16.680
And now there's war again.

00:17:17.960 --> 00:17:19.480
I really have terrible luck.

00:17:20.720 --> 00:17:21.880
You're lucky already.

00:17:22.240 --> 00:17:23.039
- We from
- If anyone needs more porridge,
- the capital garrison
- give them more.

00:17:23.920 --> 00:17:24.599
have it even worse.

00:17:25.599 --> 00:17:26.759
First we were picked

00:17:27.279 --> 00:17:28.079
to escort the envoy

00:17:28.279 --> 00:17:30.279
all the way to the northern steppe.

00:17:30.559 --> 00:17:31.279
And just before

00:17:31.440 --> 00:17:32.440
we reached the northern steppe,

00:17:33.119 --> 00:17:34.960
the Chunyuan remnants showed up

00:17:34.960 --> 00:17:35.759
trying to kill us.

00:17:36.200 --> 00:17:37.759
And it's even said the court ordered it!

00:17:40.640 --> 00:17:41.880
Isn't that Lord Chief Councilor's wife?

00:17:42.359 --> 00:17:43.519
As the Lord Chief Councilor,

00:17:44.240 --> 00:17:45.720
he actually harbors rebels

00:17:46.039 --> 00:17:47.039
and colludes with foreign enemies.

00:17:47.640 --> 00:17:48.480
So those

00:17:48.799 --> 00:17:49.960
Chunyuan remnants

00:17:50.559 --> 00:17:51.640
were publicly helping Great Yan

00:17:51.640 --> 00:17:52.759
in negotiations with Northern Barbarians,

00:17:53.240 --> 00:17:54.680
but in secret

00:17:55.359 --> 00:17:56.559
they already defected to them.

00:17:57.359 --> 00:17:58.119
Exactly.

00:17:59.799 --> 00:18:00.720
The truth

00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:02.319
is clear now.

00:18:04.119 --> 00:18:05.440
Master originally planned

00:18:05.440 --> 00:18:07.079
to use the Chunyuan remnants

00:18:07.319 --> 00:18:08.720
to deal with Northern
Barbarians' royal court.

00:18:10.319 --> 00:18:11.000
Then he'd use

00:18:11.519 --> 00:18:12.400
the Jiubian military situation

00:18:13.240 --> 00:18:14.200
to control the court.

00:18:15.319 --> 00:18:16.599
But he didn't expect

00:18:17.440 --> 00:18:19.160
to be used by Northern
Barbarians' second prince instead.

00:18:19.839 --> 00:18:21.720
All the grain and weapons here

00:18:22.279 --> 00:18:23.599
were supplied by the Chunyuan remnants

00:18:23.799 --> 00:18:24.680
to support Northern Barbarians'

00:18:25.079 --> 00:18:26.559
advance south.

00:18:30.359 --> 00:18:31.240
Master

00:18:33.119 --> 00:18:34.720
spent his whole life

00:18:35.599 --> 00:18:36.680
scheming,

00:18:38.279 --> 00:18:39.119
only to be outplayed

00:18:40.440 --> 00:18:41.880
by Northern Barbarians.

00:18:42.799 --> 00:18:43.839
Playing with fire

00:18:44.200 --> 00:18:45.279
gets you burned.

00:18:46.519 --> 00:18:47.920
Even if he was used,

00:18:48.680 --> 00:18:49.680
it's still treason.

00:18:51.680 --> 00:18:52.720
When Shi City fell,

00:18:53.720 --> 00:18:54.319
I already sent riders

00:18:54.319 --> 00:18:55.759
to report back to the capital.

00:18:56.640 --> 00:18:57.759
In less than ten days

00:18:58.240 --> 00:18:59.400
reinforcements should arrive.

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:00.680
I'm afraid

00:19:02.119 --> 00:19:03.160
that letter may

00:19:03.160 --> 00:19:04.480
never reach the court.

00:19:05.759 --> 00:19:07.359
I know Fu Hailian is powerful,

00:19:07.920 --> 00:19:09.000
but this is a foreign invasion.

00:19:09.799 --> 00:19:10.240
Would he really,

00:19:10.240 --> 00:19:11.319
just to save face,

00:19:11.839 --> 00:19:12.960
let things fall into chaos

00:19:12.960 --> 00:19:13.880
like this and do nothing?

00:19:15.599 --> 00:19:16.400
What's his plan?

00:19:17.079 --> 00:19:18.039
Surrender without a fight?

00:19:23.559 --> 00:19:24.920
He's not afraid of losing face.

00:19:25.880 --> 00:19:27.599
He's afraid of the aftermath
once the war is over.

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:29.039
Especially because

00:19:30.200 --> 00:19:31.599
he thinks I'm still alive.

00:19:33.400 --> 00:19:34.039
Report!

00:19:34.559 --> 00:19:34.960
My lord!

00:19:35.359 --> 00:19:36.119
A Northern Barbarian force

00:19:36.279 --> 00:19:37.680
is heading toward Huxiao Gorge.

00:19:40.519 --> 00:19:41.319
How many?

00:19:41.559 --> 00:19:42.400
About 800.

00:19:42.720 --> 00:19:43.799
When will they arrive?

00:19:44.200 --> 00:19:45.079
They're moving slowly

00:19:45.480 --> 00:19:46.279
and carrying supplies.

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:47.200
Roughly

00:19:47.359 --> 00:19:48.400
one hour.

00:19:58.559 --> 00:19:59.160
Ergou,

00:19:59.359 --> 00:20:00.759
your pack's already ready.

00:20:01.079 --> 00:20:01.759
Planning to run?

00:20:07.799 --> 00:20:10.079
Who said I'm running?

00:20:11.519 --> 00:20:12.160
Qingpu,

00:20:12.759 --> 00:20:13.680
go find Yanyun

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:15.559
and tell him the situation here.

00:20:16.279 --> 00:20:16.799
Yes.

00:20:27.720 --> 00:20:28.559
Yi County is the last line

00:20:28.559 --> 00:20:29.759
of defense on the border.

00:20:30.079 --> 00:20:31.279
If Yi County falls,

00:20:31.559 --> 00:20:32.079
the enemy

00:20:32.640 --> 00:20:33.720
can push straight through

00:20:34.200 --> 00:20:35.079
toward Zijing Pass.

00:20:36.039 --> 00:20:36.680
And then,

00:20:38.039 --> 00:20:39.000
they'll be

00:20:40.039 --> 00:20:41.240
at the capital gates.

00:20:43.640 --> 00:20:44.400
How many do we have?

00:20:45.759 --> 00:20:46.359
400.

00:20:46.759 --> 00:20:47.759
400 against 800.

00:20:48.720 --> 00:20:49.599
We're outnumbered,

00:20:50.359 --> 00:20:52.039
but Huxiao Gorge is steep terrain,

00:20:52.680 --> 00:20:53.480
easy to defend, hard to attack.

00:20:54.680 --> 00:20:55.599
And we're in the shadows.

00:20:58.079 --> 00:20:58.960
We might still be able to hold.

00:20:59.680 --> 00:21:00.200
Mr. Chen!

00:21:02.240 --> 00:21:02.680
Mr. Chen,

00:21:03.200 --> 00:21:04.119
some guys at the camp

00:21:04.119 --> 00:21:05.240
heard Northern Barbarians are coming

00:21:05.359 --> 00:21:06.200
and are talking about running.

00:21:06.799 --> 00:21:08.079
Madam also had Ms. Qingpu send word,

00:21:08.359 --> 00:21:09.000
saying

00:21:09.920 --> 00:21:11.079
morale's very low.

00:21:15.519 --> 00:21:16.079
Got it.

00:21:16.359 --> 00:21:17.359
I'm thinking of a way.

00:21:19.759 --> 00:21:20.279
Yes.

00:21:23.519 --> 00:21:24.279
Luckily,

00:21:24.680 --> 00:21:25.920
among these 400 men,

00:21:27.240 --> 00:21:28.200
many once followed

00:21:28.720 --> 00:21:30.119
Lord Changxing

00:21:30.119 --> 00:21:30.759
and Lord Jingyuan

00:21:30.920 --> 00:21:32.680
in battles against Northern Barbarians.

00:21:34.160 --> 00:21:34.920
What are you getting at?

00:21:41.640 --> 00:21:42.240
I want

00:21:43.480 --> 00:21:44.920
to borrow something from you.

00:21:46.799 --> 00:21:47.559
What?

00:21:49.799 --> 00:21:50.799
The Ye family name.

00:22:02.720 --> 00:22:04.119
If we don't run now, it'll be too late.

00:22:06.519 --> 00:22:07.440
Wanna leave?

00:22:07.880 --> 00:22:09.039
But none of them are leaving.

00:22:11.400 --> 00:22:12.160
If you want to go, go now!

00:22:12.720 --> 00:22:13.640
Cut the nonsense!

00:22:14.920 --> 00:22:16.160
Soldiers who flee without a fight

00:22:16.519 --> 00:22:17.440
still have the nerve to talk?

00:22:17.920 --> 00:22:18.519
Shameless!

00:22:21.319 --> 00:22:22.880
I'm just discussing it with you.

00:22:41.559 --> 00:22:43.240
Wasn't our commander surnamed Chen?

00:22:43.640 --> 00:22:44.240
What does

00:22:44.519 --> 00:22:45.480
"Ye" mean?

00:22:46.680 --> 00:22:47.440
The Ye Army?

00:23:08.960 --> 00:23:10.079
It really is the Ye Army!

00:23:10.920 --> 00:23:11.720
The Ye Army!

00:23:11.720 --> 00:23:13.240
Go, it's the Ye Army!

00:23:13.240 --> 00:23:14.440
The Ye Army!

00:23:14.680 --> 00:23:15.400
The Ye Army!

00:23:18.240 --> 00:23:18.920
It really is the Ye Army.
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:23:33.240 --> 00:23:33.839
My lord.

00:23:34.640 --> 00:23:35.759
Lord Changxing!

00:23:36.480 --> 00:23:37.400
Formation!

00:23:40.799 --> 00:23:41.759
Cao Yiming, pennon leader
of the Sixth Banner,

00:23:41.759 --> 00:23:43.240
First Division, Third Department,
Armored Cavalry Battalion,

00:23:43.359 --> 00:23:44.200
Ye Army, reporting back!

00:23:44.359 --> 00:23:45.400
Zhao Tietou,

00:23:45.599 --> 00:23:46.799
Third Banner, Third Division,
Second Department, C Infantry Battalion,

00:23:47.079 --> 00:23:47.960
reporting back!

00:23:48.240 --> 00:23:49.160
Rong Qixiang,
cart commander of the First Division,
Fourth Department,

00:23:49.960 --> 00:23:50.640
Logistics Battalion
Ye Army, reporting back!
Fourth Banner, Fifth Division,
Third Department,

00:23:51.720 --> 00:23:52.759
B Infantry Battalion, Ye Army!

00:23:52.759 --> 00:23:53.519
Li Jichang, Second Banner, Third Division,

00:23:53.519 --> 00:23:54.759
- Reporting back!
- Second Department, B Infantry Battalion,

00:23:55.000 --> 00:23:56.160
Ye Army, reporting back!

00:23:56.599 --> 00:23:57.440
Zhao Baoshan, Third Banner,

00:23:57.440 --> 00:23:58.680
Second Division, First Department,
Armored Cavalry Battalion,

00:23:58.680 --> 00:23:59.400
Ye Army, reporting back!
Jin Qianli, cart commander
of the First Division,

00:24:00.400 --> 00:24:01.039
Third Department,
Logistics Battalion

00:24:01.559 --> 00:24:02.799
Ye Army, reporting back!

00:24:11.799 --> 00:24:12.319
Very well!

00:24:17.920 --> 00:24:18.920
That armor of his…

00:24:19.960 --> 00:24:20.839
It belongs to Lord Changxing.

00:24:22.880 --> 00:24:23.519
The late emperor

00:24:24.400 --> 00:24:25.640
once specially bestowed
upon Lord Changxing

00:24:25.920 --> 00:24:26.759
a red-feathered helmet

00:24:27.039 --> 00:24:27.759
as a mark of honor
for his outstanding military achievements.

00:24:30.640 --> 00:24:31.559
Back then, Lord Changxing

00:24:32.119 --> 00:24:33.200
held the frontier with a single charge,

00:24:33.279 --> 00:24:34.160
invincible wherever he went.

00:24:34.519 --> 00:24:35.440
He struck such fear
into Northern Barbarians

00:24:35.920 --> 00:24:36.759
that they trembled at his name.

00:24:37.720 --> 00:24:38.640
And now Ye Xian

00:24:40.119 --> 00:24:40.839
has not dishonored

00:24:40.839 --> 00:24:41.920
the prestige of Lord Changxing.

00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:45.440
Let me ask you all,

00:24:45.880 --> 00:24:46.799
30 years ago,

00:24:47.400 --> 00:24:48.119
my father

00:24:48.119 --> 00:24:50.039
led the Ye Army in a bloody
battle at Suolong Pass,

00:24:50.880 --> 00:24:52.599
did he ever retreat

00:24:53.079 --> 00:24:54.200
just because his armor was not secured?

00:24:54.319 --> 00:24:57.640
Never!

00:24:57.640 --> 00:24:58.519
18 years ago,

00:24:59.079 --> 00:25:00.200
when the White River burst its banks,

00:25:01.000 --> 00:25:02.599
my father personally led his death squad

00:25:02.960 --> 00:25:04.200
to form a human wall
and protect the people.

00:25:04.880 --> 00:25:06.359
Did he ever abandon them

00:25:06.519 --> 00:25:07.759
because of the raging floodwaters?

00:25:07.759 --> 00:25:10.519
Never!

00:25:11.079 --> 00:25:12.119
Ten years ago,

00:25:12.799 --> 00:25:14.119
the 18 riders of the Black Armor Battalion

00:25:14.119 --> 00:25:15.200
crossed Cuiwei Mountain by night.

00:25:15.799 --> 00:25:17.079
Facing an enemy ten times their number,

00:25:17.440 --> 00:25:18.839
yet still slew generals
and seized banners.

00:25:19.039 --> 00:25:20.920
Did even a single Ye soldier

00:25:20.920 --> 00:25:22.440
bow his head to the barbarians?

00:25:22.640 --> 00:25:25.359
Never!

00:25:25.359 --> 00:25:25.839
Good!

00:25:26.680 --> 00:25:28.440
All of you are good boys of the Ye Army!

00:25:29.079 --> 00:25:30.599
Though Northern Barbarians
have 800 troops,

00:25:30.920 --> 00:25:32.599
our Ye Army can fight one against ten,

00:25:33.319 --> 00:25:35.279
we've never been defeated,
never feared them!

00:25:35.880 --> 00:25:36.960
Today, Lord Chen and I

00:25:36.960 --> 00:25:38.279
will lead you all
to face the enemy together.

00:25:38.640 --> 00:25:39.519
I promise you all:

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:41.160
for every enemy head taken,

00:25:41.559 --> 00:25:42.640
you will be rewarded ten taels of silver!

00:25:43.720 --> 00:25:45.000
Capture the enemy leader alive,

00:25:45.240 --> 00:25:46.359
and you will be promoted three ranks!

00:25:46.559 --> 00:25:48.240
Leave none of them alive!

00:25:48.240 --> 00:25:57.480
Kill!

00:26:05.599 --> 00:26:06.799
You must be careful.

00:26:08.359 --> 00:26:09.480
Don't you dare die.

00:26:11.279 --> 00:26:12.039
After the victory,

00:26:12.839 --> 00:26:14.079
we'll drink "Moonlit White"
together again.

00:26:14.759 --> 00:26:15.240
Alright.

00:26:17.079 --> 00:26:17.480
Take care.
Take care.

00:26:21.160 --> 00:26:21.559
Let's go.

00:26:39.160 --> 00:26:39.599
What's wrong?

00:26:40.400 --> 00:26:41.000
Nothing.

00:26:42.240 --> 00:26:43.440
I'm just thinking…

00:26:44.680 --> 00:26:45.279
If…

00:26:47.880 --> 00:26:49.160
If Lord Changxing were still alive

00:26:49.960 --> 00:26:51.279
and saw you today,

00:26:51.799 --> 00:26:52.839
he would surely be overjoyed.

00:26:59.240 --> 00:27:00.640
I'll go take a look outside.

00:27:35.400 --> 00:27:36.839
We need to cut more cloth.

00:27:38.240 --> 00:27:38.720
Alright.

00:27:39.240 --> 00:27:40.079
I'll go find more.

00:27:48.480 --> 00:27:49.960
This is all the medicine we could find.

00:27:55.680 --> 00:27:56.519
Even having this much

00:27:56.759 --> 00:27:57.839
is already good enough.

00:28:31.960 --> 00:28:32.680
Don't worry too much.

00:28:33.680 --> 00:28:34.880
Mr. Chen and Lord Ye

00:28:35.119 --> 00:28:36.279
are blessed with good fortune.

00:28:40.160 --> 00:28:40.839
Yao,

00:28:42.079 --> 00:28:42.920
I'm worried about you too.

00:28:43.839 --> 00:28:45.279
If you really run into danger,

00:28:45.880 --> 00:28:46.640
remember:

00:28:46.960 --> 00:28:47.759
leave if you can.

00:28:48.160 --> 00:28:48.960
I won't leave.

00:28:52.119 --> 00:28:53.680
Though our Ji family is only merchants,

00:28:54.279 --> 00:28:55.759
our spirit to defend the country

00:28:56.440 --> 00:28:57.759
is no less than anyone else's.

00:29:51.559 --> 00:29:52.039
Bad news.

00:29:53.359 --> 00:29:53.960
What is it, sir?

00:29:54.240 --> 00:29:55.039
There's no supply convoy.

00:29:55.599 --> 00:29:56.799
They've split the 800 troops

00:29:56.880 --> 00:29:57.680
into two units.

00:29:58.279 --> 00:29:59.640
This is the vanguard, 400 men.

00:30:00.000 --> 00:30:01.000
There are another 400 in the rear.

00:30:01.480 --> 00:30:02.039
What do we do?

00:30:02.680 --> 00:30:03.480
Changing the plan now
is too late.

00:30:04.480 --> 00:30:05.640
Proceed with the original plan.

00:30:05.640 --> 00:30:06.240
But we must be fast,
otherwise,

00:30:08.079 --> 00:30:08.640
we'll be

00:30:08.640 --> 00:30:10.119
flanked and swallowed

00:30:10.119 --> 00:30:10.920
by the other force.

00:30:12.039 --> 00:30:13.240
Go report to Lord Ye.

00:30:13.640 --> 00:30:14.119
Yes!

00:31:03.960 --> 00:31:04.759
Open fire!

00:31:08.200 --> 00:31:08.880
Form ranks!

00:31:11.440 --> 00:31:12.319
Ambush!

00:31:12.640 --> 00:31:13.440
Form ranks!

00:31:14.880 --> 00:31:15.960
Ambush!

00:31:23.920 --> 00:31:24.359
Loose arrows!
Loose arrows!

00:31:41.079 --> 00:31:41.640
Fire!

00:31:44.480 --> 00:31:45.200
Advance!

00:32:13.759 --> 00:32:20.240
Kill!

00:32:53.759 --> 00:32:55.279
Report!

00:32:57.039 --> 00:32:57.960
The enemy has been ambushed

00:32:58.200 --> 00:32:59.079
and is engaged with our forces.

00:32:59.519 --> 00:33:00.319
How is the battle going?

00:33:00.839 --> 00:33:01.599
We have the upper hand.

00:33:02.559 --> 00:33:03.039
Keep scouting.
Yes!

00:33:10.960 --> 00:33:11.680
Advance!

00:33:12.359 --> 00:33:16.799
Kill!

00:33:25.319 --> 00:33:25.880
That direction…

00:33:26.599 --> 00:33:27.319
That's Lord Ye.

00:34:14.639 --> 00:34:15.760
It's the Ye Army!

00:34:16.079 --> 00:34:17.800
Kill them!

00:34:28.039 --> 00:34:29.079
Ye Army!

00:34:29.639 --> 00:34:30.760
Advance!

00:36:17.719 --> 00:36:18.920
Archers ready!

00:36:20.920 --> 00:36:21.480
Loose!

00:36:23.039 --> 00:36:23.719
Ready!

00:36:24.280 --> 00:36:24.880
Loose!

00:36:34.480 --> 00:36:35.039
Report!

00:36:35.599 --> 00:36:36.880
The 800 enemy troops split in two!

00:36:37.119 --> 00:36:37.920
The rear force has 400 men!

00:36:38.559 --> 00:36:40.039
Lord Chen orders a quick victory!

00:37:22.360 --> 00:37:22.800
Sir!

00:37:57.960 --> 00:37:58.880
You Yan cur!

00:38:02.679 --> 00:38:03.760
I'm gonna gut you!

00:38:15.480 --> 00:38:17.000
Report!

00:38:17.400 --> 00:38:17.960
How is it?
The situation is bad.

00:38:19.039 --> 00:38:19.800
We're losing ground!

00:38:22.599 --> 00:38:23.920
Northern Barbarians
are physically stronger,

00:38:24.119 --> 00:38:25.000
one of them can fight ten.

00:38:25.679 --> 00:38:26.840
We're already a depleted force.

00:38:27.559 --> 00:38:28.719
And our firearms are gone.

00:38:29.400 --> 00:38:30.159
In close combat,

00:38:30.400 --> 00:38:31.360
we can't beat them.

00:38:33.119 --> 00:38:33.679
I'll go help.
No!

00:38:34.760 --> 00:38:35.079
Yao!
It's too dangerous!

00:38:36.119 --> 00:38:37.119
I am an official of Great Yan,

00:38:37.760 --> 00:38:38.119
I'm going.
But…

00:38:38.920 --> 00:38:39.519
No "but".

00:38:40.039 --> 00:38:40.679
Stay here

00:38:41.360 --> 00:38:42.119
and protect the civilians.

00:38:46.880 --> 00:38:47.280
You,
and you.

00:38:48.320 --> 00:38:48.760
Come with me!
Yes!
Yes!

00:39:30.599 --> 00:39:31.679
Useless.

00:39:35.119 --> 00:39:36.199
Go reinforce the rear.

00:39:36.800 --> 00:39:37.199
Yes.

00:39:39.079 --> 00:39:39.440
Let's go.

00:40:15.719 --> 00:40:16.840
Protect Lord Ye!

00:40:31.920 --> 00:40:32.559
Archers!

00:40:33.440 --> 00:40:34.280
Loose!

00:40:59.360 --> 00:41:00.440
Report!

00:41:01.079 --> 00:41:02.079
We're losing to Northern Barbarians.

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:03.119
Casualties are heavy!

00:41:03.119 --> 00:41:04.280
400 enemy reinforcements
are closing fast,

00:41:04.599 --> 00:41:05.480
less than 200 paces away.

00:41:14.239 --> 00:41:15.360
Jinzhao!

00:41:15.440 --> 00:41:16.119
You can't go!

00:41:18.320 --> 00:41:19.320
There are still so many civilians here.

00:41:20.880 --> 00:41:21.360
Are you really going to

00:41:21.360 --> 00:41:22.480
abandon them?

00:42:27.280 --> 00:42:28.400
Charge through!

00:42:53.639 --> 00:42:54.559
Young…

00:42:55.519 --> 00:42:57.000
Lord Ye

00:44:08.079 --> 00:44:08.760
Lord…

00:44:09.920 --> 00:44:10.440
Ye.

00:44:27.760 --> 00:44:28.440
Sir!

00:44:47.920 --> 00:44:48.800
Sir…

00:44:51.159 --> 00:44:52.519
you must…

00:44:53.480 --> 00:44:55.280
survive.